有些印尼佛教徒對雅加達的[佛陀酒吧](http://www.indonesiamatters.com/4264/buddhist-religious-
symbols/ "http://www.indonesiamatters.com/4264/buddhist-religious-
symbols/")（Buddha
Bar）感到不滿，他們認為這間酒吧的名稱[侮辱佛教](http://theunspunblog.com/2009/03/06/in-buddhas-
name/ "http://theunspunblog.com/2009/03/06/in-buddhas-name/")。

